A oto CSS dla podstawowej responsywnoci:

```css
.navbar {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  background-color: #333;
}

.nav-links {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  padding: 0;
}

.nav-links li {
  margin: 0 15px;
}

.nav-links a {
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .nav-links {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .nav-links li {
    margin: 10px 0;
  }
}
```
